## 📊 Dataset

The project uses a hierarchical JSON dataset representing a **Corporate Budget Distribution** across multiple departments such as:

- Engineering
- Research & Development
- Marketing
- Operations & Legal

Each department contains multiple subcategories with allocated budget values. :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}

