---

## 📖 Algorithm

This project implements the **Squarified Treemap Algorithm**, which:

- Calculates the total value of each parent node.
- Converts values into proportional rectangle areas.
- Arranges rectangles to minimize the worst aspect ratio.
- Recursively renders child nodes within parent rectangles.
- Displays labels and budget values using HTML5 Canvas. :contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}

